dc_title_s: County and municipality map of New Jersey : political boundaries revised to June 30, 1956 / Index to topographic maps
dc_description_s: New Jersey Geological Survey. County and Municipality Map of New Jersey (Atlas Sheet No. 39A) overprinted with boundaries of topographic Atlas Sheets and U.S.G.S 7.5-minute topographic quadrangles in purple. Changes recorded to January 1, 1963. "Note: The road network shown in fine black lines has not been revised." From original surveys, based on the triangulation of the U. S. Coast and Geodetic Survey; C. C. Vermeule, Topographer. The shore lines of tidal waters are mainly from the U.S.C. & G Survey. Boundary lines revised by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dc_publisher_s: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1963.
